title: Looking back and ahead at Utah's football schedule after win over ASU
text:
Utes improve to 6-0 with a 34-18 victory over Arizona State at Rice-Eccles Stadium.
Upcoming Games Utah Football Utah Utah @ USC Los Angeles Memorial Coliseum, Los Angeles Oct. 24, 5:30 p.m. 5 Days 23 Hrs 27 Mins 0 Secs More Coverage Utah football: Utes bump up to No. 3 in AP poll, hang tight at No. 7 in coaches poll Utes report card vs. Arizona State Utes remain unbeaten with 34-18 win over Arizona State Utes go to the air with Wilson on rainy night UTAH
Sept. 3 — MICHIGAN, won 24-17
Sept. 11 — UTAH STATE, won, 24-14
Sept. 19 — at Fresno State, won 45-24
Sept. 26 — at Oregon, won 62-20
Oct. 10 — CALIFORNIA, won 30-24
Oct. 17 — ARIZONA STATE, won 34-18
Oct. 24 — at USC , 5:30 p.m. (FOX)
Oct. 31 — OREGON STATE, TBA
Nov. 7 — at Washington, TBA
Nov. 14 — at Arizona, TBA
Nov. 21 — UCLA , TBA
Nov. 28 — COLORADO, TBA
All times Mountain
MICHIGAN (5-2): Lost to Michigan State, 27-23. Up next: Oct. 31 at Minnesota (4-3).
UTAH STATE (4-2): Defeated Boise State, 52-26. Up next: Friday at San Diego State (4-3).
FRESNO STATE (2-5): Defeated UNLV , 31-28. Up next: Saturday at Air Force (3-3).
OREGON (4-3, 2-2): Defeated Washington, 26-20. Up next: Oct. 29 at Arizona State (4-3, 2-2).
CALIFORNIA (5-1, 2-1): Had a bye. Up next: Thursday at UCLA (4-2, 1-2).
ARIZONA STATE (4-3, 2-2): Lost at Utah, 34-18. Up next: Oct. 29 vs. Oregon (4-3, 2-2).
USC (3-3, 1-2): Lost at Notre Dame, 41-31. Up next: Saturday vs. Utah (6-0, 3-0).
OREGON STATE (2-4, 0-3): Lost at Washington State, 52-31 . Up next: Saturday vs. Colorado (3-4, 0-3).
WASHINGTON (3-3, 1-2): Lost to Oregon, 26-20. Up next: Saturday at Stanford (5-1, 4-0).
ARIZONA (5-2, 2-2): Defeated Colorado, 38-31. Up next: Saturday vs. Washington State (4-2, 2-1).
UCLA (4-2, 1-2): Lost at Stanford, 56-35. Up next: Thursday vs. California (5-1, 2-1).
COLORADO (3-3, 0-2): Lost to Arizona, 38-31. Up next: Saturday at Oregon State (2-4, 0-3).
